    "# PSM for ice core d18O"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "18c384be-ebdf-43b2-a57c-dce31809075f",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "In this tutorial, we introduce the PSM for ice core d18O in `cfr`."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 1,
   "id": "70669673-25d3-442c-9277-a65ce61bd190",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "%load_ext autoreload\n",
    "%autoreload 2\n",
    "\n",
    "import cfr\n",
    "import pandas as pd\n",
    "import numpy as np\n",
    "import os\n",
    "\n",
    "import warnings\n",
    "warnings.filterwarnings('ignore')"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "2884da2e-d7c6-4f62-a649-cc8ba59a8aea",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Data preparation"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "d81b3e43-49c0-4020-a32d-71437df411a2",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### Proxy"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 2,
   "id": "fd06af7e-2cbc-4094-b728-d7fdf5fb810d",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "df = pd.read_pickle('./data/pages2k_dataset.pkl')\n",
    "pdb = cfr.ProxyDatabase().from_df(df)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 3,
   "id": "801fffa4-2c40-4ece-af3f-28b40f08f8ed",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "\n",
      "text/plain": [
       "<Figure size 864x288 with 2 Axes>"
      ]
     },
     "metadata": {
      "needs_background": "light"
     },
     "output_type": "display_data"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "pobj = pdb.records['Arc_011']\n",
    "fig, ax = pobj.plot()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "0e28826f-7540-4637-a34c-78f5f4ff9ad3",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### Model"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 4,
   "id": "7397f66c-f60e-406b-9a4a-daa39b103c2d",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "name": "stdout",
     "output_type": "stream",
     "text": [
      "CPU times: user 1.01 s, sys: 11.7 ms, total: 1.02 s\n",
      "Wall time: 1.03 s\n"
     ]
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "%%time\n",
    "\n",
    "dirpath = '/Volumes/ExtraDrive/Data/GCM_sims/icesm_last_millennium_historical'\n",
    "\n",
    "model_tas = cfr.ClimateField().load_nc(os.path.join(dirpath, 'tas_sfc_Amon_iCESM_past1000historical_085001-200512.nc'))\n",
    "model_pr = cfr.ClimateField().load_nc(os.path.join(dirpath, 'pr_sfc_Amon_iCESM_past1000historical_085001-200512.nc'))\n",
    "model_psl = cfr.ClimateField().load_nc(os.path.join(dirpath, 'psl_sfc_Amon_iCESM_past1000historical_085001-200512.nc'))\n",
    "model_d18O = cfr.ClimateField().load_nc(os.path.join(dirpath, 'd18O_sfc_Amon_iCESM_past1000historical_085001-200512.nc'))"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "cadc939a-62b6-4443-ae5d-e9fd0e8da887",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Get climate data for a specific `ProxyRecord`"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 5,
   "id": "aa189084-e1af-4aae-81e8-9af08dbb0b8b",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "name": "stdout",
     "output_type": "stream",
     "text": [
      "\u001b[1m\u001b[32mProxyRecord.clim deleted for Arc_011.\u001b[0m\n",
      "\u001b[1m\u001b[32mProxyRecord.clim[\"model_tas\"] created.\u001b[0m\n",
      "\u001b[1m\u001b[32mProxyRecord.clim[\"model_pr\"] created.\u001b[0m\n",
      "\u001b[1m\u001b[32mProxyRecord.clim[\"model_psl\"] created.\u001b[0m\n",
      "\u001b[1m\u001b[32mProxyRecord.clim[\"model_d18O\"] created.\u001b[0m\n",
      "CPU times: user 174 ms, sys: 249 ms, total: 423 ms\n",
      "Wall time: 425 ms\n"
     ]
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "%%time\n",
    "\n",
    "pobj.del_clim()\n",
    "pobj.get_clim(model_tas, tag='model')\n",
    "pobj.get_clim(model_pr, tag='model')\n",
    "pobj.get_clim(model_psl, tag='model')\n",
    "pobj.get_clim(model_d18O, tag='model')"
   ]
  },
